Interface Specialized

All Known Subinterfaces:
Edge, Element, Node, TreeNode
All Known Implementing Classes:
ALDataEdge, ALDataNode, ALEdge, ALNode, ALReadOnlyDataEdge, ALReadOnlyDataNode, ElementAdapter, SimpleDataTreeNode, SimpleReadOnlyDataTreeNode, SimpleTreeNode, TreeGraphDataNode, TreeGraphNode, TreeGraphReadOnlyDataNode
public interface Specialized
An interface for specialisations of Node, TreeNode and Edge that may have a named sub-class (called label). This method returns the subclass name.
Author:
Jacques Gignoux - 15 avr. 2019
